## Problem
Multi-profile config is only raw JSON text areas (`profileDisplayNamesJson`, `enabledProfilesJson`, `visibleWindowsJson`, `customProfilesJson`). Invalid JSON silently falls back via `parseJsonConfig` to `[]`/`{}` (all enabled / no renames), with no validation feedback. Design spec required a discovered-profile table (enable checkbox, display name, path, rediscover) and window checkboxes — not free-form JSON.

## Location
contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:264-290

## Suggested fix
Implement the designed Profiles / Visible quotas sections; keep JSON only as advanced/export if needed. Validate on Apply and show parse errors.

